Key Match Events: Algeria fell behind early following a lapse in concentration but recovered to win 5-1
Houssem Aouar posed a huge threat on the wing
Thibault Kludge opened the scoring for Togo in the 11th minute
Said Behrahma equalised for Algeria in the 29th minute
Benhrahma completed his brace by netting a penalty in the 55th minute
Goals from Aouar, Amine Gouiri, and Mohamed Amoura secured the win for Algeria
The win keeps Algeria at the top of Group E in the qualifiers
